Class NoSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • evSOLve.JEvolution.selection.Selection
      • evSOLve.JEvolution.selection.NoSelection

  • public class NoSelection
extends Selection
    All parents are selected into the next generation, i.e., there is no selection pressure (JEvolution native selection).
